<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4776873>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Species of Schizophrys White, 1848. A, Schizophrys serratus White, 1848 syntype (from White, 1848: 223, unnumbered fig.), “Isle of France” (= Mauritius); B, Mithrax asper H. Milne Edwards, 1831, lectotype (herein designated), female (carapace width × carapace length: 25.1 × 29.3 mm) (MNHN-IU-B463), no locality (photographed by N.K. Ng)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4776873/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

